title:

tags:

Each tag up to 20 characters.

currency_code: The ISO (alphabetic) code for the items currency
quantity: The quantity of this item available for sale

is_customizable:

(No = 0 | Yes = 1)
taxonomy_id:
The numeric ID of the listing main category.
(This will automatically update depending on the Category you select)
Do Not Edit
shipping_template_id: The numeric ID of the shipping template associated with the listing
is_supply:
If your item is a supply item, Select TRUE
If your item is a finished product, Select FALSE
